messages.messageBody:
LOL My house is ALIVE...with the sound of MUSIC! The deed is done...Sarah now has her guitar, and Logan has a drum.

I get to order my flute shortly! Can't wait! I've found all of the recorders, and tomorrow we're going to go get a small bondo drum set and one of those band-in-a-box things with cymbals, clapper, triangle and rhythm sticks; and a set of jingle bells.

MamaBeth
